The evidence with the title 'Fake video claims that Modi didn't care while man was dying behind ... ' says Mar 27, 2018  ...  ... Narendra Modi was giving a speech is doing the rounds, claiming that the prime minister ignored the 'dying' man.  ... However, the man behind was neither part of Modi's security detail, and nor did he die of a heart attack.  ... (it doesn't matter if someone is dying, Modiji will continue to give his speech.). 
